Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:03.13,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I know the world can get you down
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.05,0:00:08.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Things don't work out quite the way that you tho-o-ought
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.32,0:00:12.21,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Feeling like all your best days a-are done
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.66,0:00:15.21,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Your fears and doubts are all you've got
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.22,0:00:20.23,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But there's a li-ight shining deep inside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.35,0:00:23.46,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Beneath those fears and doubts, so just squash 'em
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:28.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And let it shine for all the world to see
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.45,0:00:31.37,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That it is time, yeah, time to be awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.60,0:00:33.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Ah, ah-ah, awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.25,0:00:35.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It's time to be so awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.27,0:00:37.22,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Ah ah, ah-ah, awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:39.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It's time to be so awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.58,0:00:41.65,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You've no idea how hard it's been
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.71,0:00:46.97,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This dull routi-ine we've been fo-orced to do-o
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.76,0:00:50.91,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Don't let them ro-ob you of who you are
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:54.02,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Be awesome, it's all up to you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.81,0:00:58.78,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I feel the li-ight stirring deep insi-ide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.90,0:01:02.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It's like a tale sti-i-ill yet to be to-o-old
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:06.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And now it's time to break the shackles free
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.07,0:01:09.77,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And start living like the brave and the bold
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.85,0:01:11.65,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It's time to be awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:13.82,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Let loose, be true, so awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.93,0:01:15.88,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It's time to be awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:17.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Go big, be you, so awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.95,0:01:21.55,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We used to soar through the clouds in the skies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.77,0:01:25.60,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Elaborate schemes we would love to devise
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.86,0:01:29.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We rescued our treasure and stored it away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:33.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Sa-avi-ing those gemstones for a rainy day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.47,0:01:37.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We see that li-ight filling up our ski-es
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.52,0:01:40.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So take the Storm King's orders and toss 'em
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.57,0:01:45.55,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Cause it's the time to let our colors fly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:49.26,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Hey, scallywags, it's time to be awesome
